aqua_affinity.Discription: Speeds up how fast you can mine blocks underwater

channeling.Discription: Summons a lightning bolt at a targeted mob when enchanted item is thrown (targeted mob must be standing in raining)

curse_of_binding.Discription: Cursed item can not be removed from player

curse_of_vanishing.Discription: Cursed item will disappear after player dies

depth_strider.Discription: Speeds up how fast you can move underwater

efficiency.Discription: Increases how fast you can mine

fire_protection.Discription: Reduces damage caused by fire and lava

frost_walker.Discription: Freezes water into ice so that you can walk on it (and also allows you to walk on magma blocks without taking damage)

impaling.Discription: Increases attack damage against sea creatures

infinity.Discription: Shoots an infinite amount of arrows

looting.Discription: Increases amount of loot dropped when mob is killed

loyalty.Discription: Returns your weapon when it is thrown like a spear

luck_of_the_sea.Discription: Increases chances of catching valuable items

lure.Discription: Increases the rate of fish biting your hook

mending.Discription: Uses xp to mend your tools, weapons and armor

multishot.Discription: Shoots 3 arrows at once but only costs 1 arrow (from your inventory)

piercing.Discription: Arrow can pierce through multiple entities

projectile_protection.Discription: Reduces projectile damage (arrows, fireballs, fire charges)

protection.Discription: General protection against attacks, fire, lava, and falling

quick_charge.Discription: Reduces the amount of time to reload a crossbow

riptide.Discription: Propels the player forward when enchanted item is thrown while in water or rain

sharpness.Discription: Increases attack damage dealt to mobs

smite.Discription: Increases attack damage against undead mobs

soul_speed.Discription: Speeds up how fast you can move across soul sand and soul soil
